11. Job Selection Algorithm
score =
    (job.priority * P_WEIGHT)
  + (urgency_flag ? U_BONUS : 0)
  + (skill_match * S_WEIGHT)
  - (distance * D_WEIGHT)
Rules
Ignore reserved/invalid jobs
Select highest score
Reserve before movement
